quoteText: When you interact with the Service, we also may use various technologies, including cookies, web beacons, pixel tags, log files, local shared objects (Flash cookies), HTML5 cookies, or other tracking technologies,
title: The service may use tracking pixels, web beacons, browser fingerprinting, and/or device fingerprinting on users.
